    "steam_appid": 3253930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/1349382a6f0b61e90b43390e4fe9511c.poster.avif?t=1772250147\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/1349382a6f0b61e90b43390e4fe9511c.webm?t=1772250147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/1349382a6f0b61e90b43390e4fe9511c.mp4?t=1772250147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵《节奏旅社》是一款搞怪、无厘头、欢乐又魔性的节奏游戏！简单操作，一键上头，丰富人物，爆笑剧情。游戏试玩 Demo 提供了多个看似莫名其妙，却又充满黑色幽默的节奏挑战，让大家提前领略这座充满奇思妙想与动感节拍的奇幻旅社！而完整版更是会有超过20个剧情迥异、玩法独特的魔性节奏游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敬请关注 🎵<strong>《节奏旅社》</strong>🎵 ，一键开启魔性抖脚的节奏之旅~ 🤪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/08d6420fd8a28b607f9f314ae0b75f8a.poster.avif?t=1772250147\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/08d6420fd8a28b607f9f314ae0b75f8a.webm?t=1772250147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/08d6420fd8a28b607f9f314ae0b75f8a.mp4?t=1772250147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单操作，一键上头</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥  游戏操作极致简单，所有关卡贯彻“一键”理念。单键的核心设计，让指尖直觉先行于大脑思考，身体比意识更早陷入魔性律动！甚至闭着眼睛，也能将节奏玩转于你的指尖。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富人物，爆笑剧情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥  旅社里住满了来自古今中外的怪咖住客，带着他们令人捧腹的爆笑故事和独一无二的“专属节奏技”，开启搞怪无厘头的节奏之旅，每一次敲击都充满了意外和惊喜。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>层层升级的节奏考验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥  游戏中每个关卡都不同类型的节奏挑战，从节奏感知、节奏记忆与操作精准度，叠加各种复合机制，从各个维度对节奏感进行综合考验，助你成为节奏达人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>音乐宇宙，无限扩展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥  融合全球多元音乐风格，从动感电音、复古迪斯科到洗脑神曲、搞怪音效，任何音乐风格都能玩转节奏。未来还将推出关卡编辑器，发挥你的创意，设计属于你自己的搞怪剧情和魔性节奏关卡，接受全球玩家的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/39bd794fbac3c97f62f6f36fe7eccd99.poster.avif?t=1772250147\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/39bd794fbac3c97f62f6f36fe7eccd99.webm?t=1772250147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/39bd794fbac3c97f62f6f36fe7eccd99.mp4?t=1772250147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作组的话</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵 我们是一家从节奏游戏起步、却不止于节奏的3人独立游戏工作室。我们想从节奏出发，持续探索音游类型的边界，寻找不同机制、风格、情绪之间的融合方式。闭上眼睛，听声音捕捉节拍，让指尖跟随旋律起舞；睁开眼睛，会发现每一次敲击都会触发意想不到的剧情展开。拒绝套路化，我们希望《节奏旅社》能给大家带来全新的体验感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵 游戏目前正在制作中，计划年底发售。如果您对《节奏旅社》感兴趣，不妨先<strong>「添加愿望单」</strong>，你的支持，将给与我们莫大的鼓舞，是我们爆肝的动力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快乐至上！ 我们想用最简单的方式，让大家在游戏中收获纯粹的欢乐！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/1a198d3488b20cd7edb7cd1ab948c326.poster.avif?t=1772250147\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253930/extras/1a198d3488b20cd7edb7cd1ab948c326.webm?t=1772250147\" type